            "body": "Reworked this toward the `on_list` approach suggested above: the default LSP location aggregation is restored, and the PR now documents an opt-in `vim.list.unique()` example for deduplicating quickfix/location-list entries.\n\nValidation:\n\n```console\ngit diff --check HEAD~1..HEAD\n```\n\nI also checked the touched doc/source files for accidental NUL bytes. I could not run `make lintdoc` in this checkout because there is no local `nvim` executable available.",
